:Merl_Hello_L:  Welcome to the #limbo-challenge! :Merl_Hello_R: 

How low can you go? 

Some builds reach epic heights! This round, we’re gonna stay down to Earth :earth2: 

Keep your blocks under the height of four, 
but let your dreams and ideas soar!

⏲️ Challenge dates: June 2- June 15 at 6 PM PDT

__Challenge Guidelines__
:earth: Your creation must be built entirely by you and in Minecraft Earth.
:crafting_table: Your build must be a brand new creation, crafted just for this challenge.
:buildplate: Build your imagination! Challenge theme is open to interpretation and buildplate size won’t be a factor in judging.
:sign: Post your images or video submission and buildplate share link in #limbo-challenge  by the deadline. Feel free to ask a Moderator to pin it!
:challenges: Winning submissions may be used in social media posts.
:fast_parrot: Have fun!
